# Set @host to the app-api address shown in the Aspire dashboard.
@host = http://localhost:5086

### 1) Upload a PDF (multipart). Change the path to a real .pdf on your machine.
POST {{host}}/api/documents/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.pdf"
Content-Type: application/pdf

< /Users/nurdanmamus/Desktop/sample.pdf
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 2) Ask a question (RAG) — searches all documents
POST {{host}}/api/chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Bu dökümanların ana konusu nedir?"
}

### 3) Ask a question limited to one document (by its Id)
POST {{host}}/api/chat/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Ödeme koşulları nelerdir?",
  "documentId": 1
}
